void SET_PED_MAX_TIME_UNDERWATER(Ped ped, float value);Parameters:ped: Ped id.value: Time in seconds. Maximum is 50.0, any value above will be changed to 50.0.Set the maximum time a ped can stay underwater. Maximum seems to be 50 seconds.
